question: @ anon taylor is the bestest ninja ever, she could have been on set to shoot one month but for sure she's been in the studio for recording and previously for the rehearsal!
answer:
Anonymous said: The dancers didn’t film for 7 months as the production has only lasted around 3 & ½ months. The remaining time it was probably rehearsals and such during pre-production. It did seem like Taylor was filming for about a month but we don’t know exactly just like we don’t know how much time she spent in pre-production as well. Obviously everybody had different schedules and requirements depending on their role.

Anonymous said: Some dancers are still working today. See @diva_y and @nicolebondzie IG stories, they say today is their last day. So it seems they’ve all been wrapping up on different days over the last week or so

Yeah… you guys, previous anon, me - we’re all just guessing. I think it’s very important to remember that we only get the impression that we know about celebrities or their schedules or whatever. Which is cool cause we don’t need to know all the details and at the end of the day we all need our own freedom and privacy…  =)
